# Unity 檔案應該以二進位模式處理
*.unity binary
*.prefab binary
*.asset binary
*.mat binary
*.anim binary
*.controller binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.tga binary
*.psd binary
*.fbx binary
*.FBX binary
*.wav binary
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary

# 文字檔案保持文字模式
*.cs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.meta text eol=lf